Two suspects are due to appear before Ngcobo Magistrate Court on Tuesday for murder. It is alleged that the woman (25) was driving her vehicle at Caca A/A when, on her way, she experienced difficulties with her vehicle. Two men aged between 35 and 45 years came pretending to offer their assistance however they drew a 9 mm pistol, shooting the woman multiple times. The woman was then taken to All Saints hospital by the members of the community where she later died as a result of her injuries. During the arrest, firearms with live ammunition were also recovered. -TNA Reporter